					for you somewhere in the home page. You can get to it by solving
					this riddle that I collabed with ChatGPT on.
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="relative w-14 h-14 translate-y-[50%] mx-auto p-2 rounded-full text-yellow bg-black z-[1]">
				<Icon name="mdi:egg-easter"/>
			</div>
			<div class="relative ml-[10px] mb-[10px] border-[3px] border-black px-5 py-10 rounded-xl space-y-5 font-dmMono text-base/tight text-left bg-[radial-gradient(#D9D9D9_1px,#F2F2F2_0)] bg-[length:5px_5px] bg-repeat">
				<div
					class="absolute inset-[10px_10px_-10px_-10px] content-[''] rounded-xl bg-[repeating-linear-gradient(-45deg,black_0_3px,transparent_0_10px)] z-[-1]"
				/>

				<p>
					In my digital realm, where ideas take flight,<br /> A tale of an apple, let me recite.
				</p>

				<p>
					Newton's revelation, a symbol well-known, <br /> Where gravity's pull was clearly shown.
				</p>

				<p>
					Seek not the apple that fell from that tree,<br /> But the iconic bitten apple, of high pedigree. 
				</p>

				<p>
					Within 2d-me, this secret you'll find,<br /> On the shell of the vessel, where my logic, magic, and art intertwine.
				</p>

				<p>
					On my trusty old laptop, where I strive to thrive,<br /> With bytes and bites, my code comes alive.
				</p>

				<p>
					A play on words, a subtle delight.<br /> In the form of a button, I've hidden from sight.
				</p>

				<p>
					Look closely, explorer, with careful attention,<br /> For a cursor, on hover, masking the hidden intention.
				</p>

				<p>
					Fire the onclick event, to unveil the unseen,<br /> My loyal companions, that make my soul gleam.  
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
